      "title": "SLFP meets the President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided to meet President Ranil Wickramasinghe today (28th) to discuss the proposals of an all-party government.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena, chairman of the Sri Lanka National Party, said this at the press conference held today (28th) at the party headquarters."
